the%20ancient%20city-state%20of%20Athens%2C%20now%20the%20Greek%20capital%2C%20around%20500%20BC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStriking%20nostalgic%20notes%2C%20the%20PM%20also%20recalled%20his%20first%20memories%20of%20the%20old%20Parliament%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-75-special-parliament-session-begins-today-10-facts-4399357%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParliament%20Special%20Session%20Begins%2C%20PM%20Addresses%20Lok%20Sabha%3A%2010%20Facts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20entered...%20as%20an%20MP...%20I%20bowed%20down%20and%20honoured%20the%20'Temple%20of%20Democracy.%20It%20was%20an%20emotional%20moment...%20I%20could%20have%20never%20imagined%20a%20child%20from%20a%20poor%20family%2C%20living%20on%20the%20railway%20platform%2C%20would%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20enter%20Parliament.%20I%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20get%20so%20much%20love...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20us%20are%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20this%20historic%20building.%20Before%20Independence%2C%20this%20was%20the%20place%20for%20the%20Imperial%20Legislative%20Council.%20After%20Independence%2C%20this%20gained%20the%20identity%20of%20Parliament.%20It%20is%20true%20the%20decision%20to%20construct%20this%20building%20was%20taken%20by%20foreign%20rulers%20but%20we%20can%20proudly%20say%20the%20toil%2C%20hard%20work%20and%20money%20that%20went%20into%20the%20construction%20was%20that%20of%20(our)%20countrymen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20praised%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20Moon%20mission%20and%20said%20India%20had%20%26quot%3Bmade%20the%20world%20proud...%20highlighted%20a%20new%20form%20of%20India's%20strength%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20and%20attributed%20it%20to%20%26quot%3B%20140%20crore%20citizens...%20not%20any%20individual%20or%20party%26quot%3B.%3C%2