peg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18131728%2FH2018111758061.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18131728%2FH2018111758061-300x230.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18131728%2FH2018111758061-1024x783.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673483%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22918%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20attending%20the%20Inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%2C%20in%20Male%2C%20Maldives%20on%20November%2017%2C%202018.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D1553060%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejoint%20India-Maldives%20press%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20issued%20after%20the%20visit%20directly%20referred%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Crenewal%20of%20the%20close%20bonds%20of%20cooperation%20and%20friendship%20with%20the%20election%20of%20Mr%20Solih%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%20It%20even%20specifically%20mentions%20that%20Solih%20requested%20help%20from%20India%20to%20support%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20government%20in%20meeting%20its%20pledges%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%20India%20eagerly%20jumped%20in%2C%20announcing%20a%20series%20of%20development%20projects%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20outlying%20islands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20Solih%20went%20on%20an%20inauguration%20spree%20of%20small%20projects%20around%20Maldives%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20round%2C%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHCIMaldives%2Fstatus%2F1696812319186255901%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20sponsored%20by%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20I