se-one-of-the-thilamale-bridge-to-be-completed-this-year%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erevised%20to%20mid-2024%20due%20to%20delays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20agreement%20to%20develop%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Futhuru-thilafalhu-utf-harbour-project-maldives-india-male-delhi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUthuru%20Thilafalhu%20atoll%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20naval%20dockyard%20for%20Maldives%20fuelled%20thousands%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20even%20as%20Mal%C3%A9%20went%20on%20the%20defensive%20amidst%20domestic%20calls%20for%20releasing%20the%20full%20details%20of%20the%20agreement.%20The%20Maldivian%20National%20Defence%20Forces%20arranged%20a%20trip%20of%20local%20journalists%20this%20weekend%20to%20the%20atoll%20to%20refute%20allegations%20that%20it%20will%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20Indian%20base.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20India%20apparently%20resonating%20among%20voters%2C%20there%20is%20now%20a%20question%20mark%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20diplomacy%20in%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20India%20has%20caused%20to%20worry%20about%20relations%20under%20a%20Muizzu%20presidency%2C%20observers%20are%20also%20not%20convinced%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20smooth%20ride%20for%20a%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20presidency.%20Even%20after%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20judiciary%20will%20not%20accept%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20to%20stand%20for%20election%20due%20to%20conviction%2C%20his%20first%20choice%20had%20been%20to%20ask%20his%20party%20to%20boycott%20the%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20housing%20minister%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20and%20join%20the%20alliance%20partner