icc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fvirat-kohli-faced-it-rahul-dravid-faced-it-in-2007-gautam-gambhirs-warning-for-rohit-sharma-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4399232%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fvirat-kohli-faced-it-rahul-dravid-faced-it-in-2007-gautam-gambhirs-warning-for-rohit-sharma-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4399232%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fvirat-kohli-faced-it-rahul-dravid-faced-it-in-2007-gautam-gambhirs-warning-for-rohit-sharma-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4399232%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Left%20Blow%20To%20INDIA%20Unity%3F%20No%20Bengal%2C%20Kerala%20Tie-Ups%2C%20Say%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20predictable%20setback%20for%20the%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20the%20CPI-M%20has%20reportedly%20decided%20against%20alliances%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%2C%20where%20its%20main%20rivals%20are%20its%20INDIA%20partners%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20name%20any%20representative%20for%20coordination%20meetings%20of%20the%20anti-BJP%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20has%2C%20sources%20say%2C%20decided%20to%20maintain%20a%20distance%20from%20%26quot%3Bboth%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Trinamool%26quot%3B%20in%20Bengal%2C%20exposing%20the%20fault%20lines%20in%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20that%20aims%20to%20fight%20unitedly%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20next%20year's%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decisions%20were%20taken%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20CPM's%20politburo%20in%20Delhi%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20decisions%20are%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20to%20ensure%20no%20division%20of%20opposition%20votes%2C%20the%20sources%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20INDIA%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20last%20week%3B%20a%20seat%20was%20kept%20vacant%20in%20the%2014-member%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Left's%20decision%2C%20though%20surprising%2C%20may%20not%20unsettle%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20given%20her%20prior%20expression%20of%20discomfort%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20sharing%20a%20stage%20with%20Left%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20politburo's%20statement%20after%20the%20meeting%20does%20not%20spell%20out%20these%20decisions.%20On%20record%2C%20it%20said%20it%20would%20work%20for%20the%20consolidation%20and%20expansion%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Polit%20Bureau%20decided%20to%20work%20for%20the%20further%20consolidation%20and%20expansion%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20strengthen%20the%20efforts%20to%20safeguard%20the%20secular%20democratic%20character%20of%20the%20Indian%20Republic%2C%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Democracy%20and%20People's%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20civil%20liberties.%20This%20requires%20that%20the%20BJP%20must%20be%20kept%20away%20from%20controlling%20the%20union%20government%20and%20state%20power.%20The%20Polit%20Bureau%20decided%20to%20further%20strengthen%20these%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20politburo%20said%20it%20also%20endorsed%20the%20party's%20stand%20in%20the%20last%20three%20meetings%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Patna%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai%20to%20organise%20a%20series%20of%20public%20meetings%20across%20the%20country%20and%20to%20mobilize%20the%20people%20to%20ensure%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20did%20indicate%20its%20reservations%20over%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20%26quot%3Borganisational%20structures%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20all%20decisions%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20constituents%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20organisational%20structures%20that%20will%20be%20an%20impediment%20for%20such%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20refused%20to%20name%20its%20representative%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Coordination%20and%20Election%20Strategy%20committee%20after%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath%20scrapped%20the%20INDIA%20rally%20in%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM-Mamata%20Banerjee%20rivalry%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20complicated%20relationships%20that%20plague%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20formed%20in%20July%20with%20the%20name%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance).%20The%20other%20is%20the%20Congress%20vs%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20feud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%2C%20according%20to%20reports%2C%20had%20conveyed%20to%20his%20leadership%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20an%20INDIA%20rally%20when%20AAP%20had%20announced%20candidates%20against%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20polls%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695021360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2F3d23c5vg_sitaram-yechury-pti_625x300_24_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-sitaram-yechury-kerala-left-blow-to-india-unity-no-bengal-kerala-tie-ups-say-sources-4400096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20huge%20blow%20to%20the%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20the%20CPI-M%20has%20reportedly%20decided%20against%20alliances%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%2C%20where%20its%20main%20rivals%20are%20its%20INDIA%20partners%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-sitaram-yechury-kerala-left-blow-to-india-unity-no-bengal-kerala-tie-ups-say-sources-4400096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-sitaram-yechury-kerala-left-blow-to-india-unity-no-bengal-kerala-tie-ups-say-sources-4400096%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%