on-emotional-moment-to-leave-old-parliament-says-pm-modi-123091800302_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Always%20Inspire%20Us%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Remembers%20Nehru's%20'Tryst%20With%20Destiny'%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20echo%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20historic%20'A%20tryst%20with%20destiny'%20speech%20in%20Parliament%20will%20continue%20to%20inspire%20the%20country's%20elected%20representatives%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20tracing%20the%20nearly%20eight-decade%20journey%20of%20the%20old%20Parliament%20building%20that%20has%20also%20been%20the%20country's%20journey%20following%20its%20Independence%20from%20British%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20nation%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Nehru%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20stroke%20of%20the%20midnight%20hour%2C%20when%20the%20world%20sleeps%2C%20India%20will%20awake%20to%20life%20and%20freedom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20echo%20of%20Nehru%20ji's%20Stroke%20of%20Midnight%20speech%20will%20inspire%20us.%20It%20is%20also%20in%20this%20House%20where%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20said%20governments%20will%20come%20and%20go%2C%20but%20this%20country%20will%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20today%20as%20he%20listed%20key%20milestones%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20old%20Parliament%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Parliament%20today%20met%20for%20a%20five-day%20special%20session%2C%20which%20would%20also%20witness%20the%20transfer%20of%20proceedings%20to%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20Today%20is%20the%20last%20day%20of%20proceedings%20at%20the%20old%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20this%20is%20an%20occasion%20to%20remember%20everyone%20who%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20Parliament's%20historic%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tribute%20to%20former%20Presidents%20and%20forme