tualArt%20for%20the%20artwork%20Village%20Group%2C%20sold%20at%20English%20auction%20house%20Sotheby's%20as%20early%20as%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20born%20in%20Budapest%20in%201913.%20Her%20father%2C%20Umrao%20Singh%20Sher-Gil%2C%20belonged%20to%20an%20aristocratic%20family%20in%20Punjab%20and%20was%20a%20scholar%20of%20Sanskrit%20and%20Persian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Sher-Gil's%20mother%20Marie%20Antoinette%20was%20a%20Hungarian%20national%20and%20trained%20opera%20singer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Sher-Gil%20showed%20interest%20in%20painting%20and%20drawing%20at%20the%20age%20of%20five.%20Her%20early%20works%2C%20in%20watercolours%2C%20showed%20vibrant%20illustrations%20of%20Hungarian%20fairy%20tales%20with%20captivating%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sher-Gil%20family%20came%20to%20India%20in%201921%20and%20settled%20in%20Shimla.%20The%20artist%20died%20in%201941%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695018720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ffikkgta_amrita-shergil-paintain-auction-1200_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famrita-sher-gils-the-story-teller-fetches-record-rs-61-8-crore-at-auction-4400005%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amrita%20Sher-Gil%20was%20a%20Sikh-Hungarian%20painter%20who%20created%20many%20stunning%20artworks.%20She%20is%20among%20the%20most%20famous%20Indian%20painters%20across%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famrita-sher-gils-the-story-teller-fetches-record-rs-61-8-crore-at-auction-4400005%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famrita-sher-gils-the-story-teller-fetches-record-rs-61-8-crore-at-auction-4400005%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famrita-sher-gils-the-story-teller-fetches-record-rs-61-8-crore-at-auction-440