l%20report%20has%20also%20noted%2C%20with%20the%20example%20of%20this%20Thoubal%20incident%2C%20that%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20local%20magistrates%20often%20do%20not%20visit%20such%20incident%20spots%2C%20demonstrating%20what%20the%20RAF%20calls%20is%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20insensitivity%20and%20lack%20of%20coordination%20resulting%20in%20mismanaged%20crowd%20control%20and%20handling%20of%20serious%20conflicts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20RAF%20is%20trained%20to%20use%20minimal%20fire%20power%20and%20is%20meant%20to%20act%20quickly%20to%20diffuse%20situations%20with%20%E2%80%9Cminimal%20lethality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20RAF%20is%20unarmed%20and%20their%20deployment%20in%20Manipur%20is%20%E2%80%9Cexposing%20them%20as%20a%20bigger%20target%20for%20firearms%20of%20miscreants%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManipur%20Police%20and%20the%20central%20forces%20have%20emerged%20at%20odds%20with%20each%20other%2C%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community%20accusing%20the%20former%20of%20siding%20with%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Meitei%20community%20accusing%20the%20latter%20of%20favouring%20Kukis.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20personnel%20of%20the%209th%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3Ebattalion%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695015945000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18111206%2FF3f08SBWcAEV7mk.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-raf-police-paramilitary-riot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hindu%20has%20reported%20that%20it%20was%20told%20by%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20that%20continuous%20exposure%20of%20