nMoD%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUYgDqhW51b%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FUYgDqhW51b%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20PRO%2C%20Kohima%20%26amp%3B%20Imphal%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(%40prodefkohima)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprodefkohima%2Fstatus%2F1703418624260886887%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThangthang%E2%80%99s%20family%20says%20that%20three%20unknown%20people%20knocked%20at%20the%20door%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20house%20on%20Saturday%20and%20took%20him%20away%20at%20gunpoint%20in%20a%20white%20car.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20that%20time%20Thangthang%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20porch%20with%20his%20son%2C%20who%20is%20seven%20years%20old.%20The%20child%20witnessed%20his%20father%20being%20led%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Thangthang%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%2C%20Reverend%20Pachung%20Serto%20Litan%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20one%20bullet%20in%20his%20head%20when%20we%20found%20his%20body%20lying%20on%20the%20street.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20knew%20who%20might%20have%20killed%20Thangthang%2C%20Litan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20did%20this%2C%20but%20we%20suspect%20people%20from%20the%20valley.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThangthang%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Kom%20community%2C%20to%20which%20famed%20boxer%20Mary%20Kom%20belongs.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Kom%20community%20with%20whom%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20and%20who%20requested%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20heard%20the%20gunshot%20on%20the%20same%20day%20at%2011%20am%2C%20but%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20it%20was%20Thang.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20family%2C%20after%20learning%20that%20ThangThang%20was%20abducted%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20several%20police%20stations%20including%20the%20Imphal%20West%20superintendent%20of%20police%20for%20help%2C%20along%20with%20all%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20including%20the%20influential%20COCOMI%20(Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMembers%20of%20Thangthang%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20others%20in%20the%20Kom%20community%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Imphal%20Police%20allegedly%20conducted%20several%20search%20operations%20in%20all%20the%20nearby%20areas%20after%20he%20was%20abducted%20in%20the%20white%20car%2C%20but%20ultimately%20failed%20to%20find%20him%20on%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Committee%20for%20Tribal%20Union%20(COTU)%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20demanded%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20reimpose%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20in%20Imphal%20Valley.%20The%20statement%20said%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20barbaric%20acts%20perpetrated%20in%20broad%20daylight%20show%20how%20the%20armed%20Meitei%20miscreants%20are%20allowed%20to%20roam%20freely%20around%20Imphal%20Valley%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20activities%20without%20hesitation%2C%20once%20again%20proving%20that%20Manipur%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20state%20run%20by%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government%20but%20is%20run%20by%20communal-minded%20autocratic%20rulers.%20As%20the%20state%20police%20failed%20to%20perform%20its%20duties%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20Reimposition%20of%20AFSPA%20in%20the%20valley%20would%20be%20the%20only%20way%20out%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20contain%20the%20armed%20Meiteis%20from%20carrying%20out%20such%20inhumane%20acts%20against%20innocent%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20Border%20Security%20Forces%20jawans%20and%20several%20c