rs.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20age%20of%20women%20at%20first%20marriage%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20about%2030%20years%20old%2C%20according%20to%20Statistica.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F371933%2Fmedian-age-of-us-americans-at-their-first-wedding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorresponding%20age%20for%20women%20is%20around%2028%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20are%20delaying%20childbirth.%20The%20median%20age%20at%20which%20women%20had%20their%20first%20child%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20increased%20from%2026.6%20years%20in%201986%20to%2031.8%20years%20in%202018%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eoc.org.hk%2Feoc%2FUpload%2FUserFiles%2FFile%2FFactSheet%2FFamilyFactSheetEng.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEqual%20Opportunities%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20published%20in%20August%20by%20the%20Family%20Planning%20Association%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F3231195%2Fchildless-hong-kong-couples-double-5-years-average-births-drop-below-1-family-first-time%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20number%20of%20children%20among%20the%20city's%20couples%20dropped%20to%20a%20new%20low%20of%200.9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20of%20the%20millennials%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20expressed%20a%20similar%20sentiment%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20childbirth%3A%20It's%20prohibitively%20expensive%20to%20raise%20a%20child%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENg%2C%20who%20is%20unmarried%20and%20has%20no%20children%2C%20said%20financial%20concerns%20will%20play%20a%20big%20part%20in%20her%20decision%20whether%20to%20have%20kids%20or%20not.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20consider%20getting%20married%2C%20but%20as%20for