%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Feng%2Ffaq%2Fmarriage-registration.html%23marriage_reg_q2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20recognized%20in%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20same-sex%20partners%20do%20have%20equal%20parental%20rights%20over%20their%20children%2C%20are%20eligible%20for%20dependent%20visas%2C%20and%20can%20elect%20for%20joint%20tax%20assessment%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongfp.com%2F2021%2F06%2F11%2Fhong-kongs-lgbt-community-hails-step-forward-as-court-grants-parental-rights-for-same-sex-partners%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHong%20Kong%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hong%20Kong's%20top%20court%20recently%20ordered%20the%20city's%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20new%20system%20that%20can%20legally%20recognize%20same-sex%20couples%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Fchina%2Fsame-sex-marriage-ruling-hong-kong-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20considered%20a%20victory%20for%20LGBTQ%2B%20activists%20in%20the%20city%2C%20though%20the%20decision%20didn't%20include%20fulfilling%20their%20demands%20for%20full%20marriage%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20locksmith%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20married%20and%20has%20one%20kid%20on%20the%20way.%20The%20news%20was%20%26quot%3Bunexpected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%20Despite%20his%20growing%20household%2C%20he%20says%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20move%20somewhere%20larger%2C%20or%20get%20another%20job%2C%20after%20he%20has%20his%20first%20kid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHong%20Kong's%20millennials%20are%20similar%20to%20their%20global%20counterparts%20in%20many%20ways.%20They're%20getting%20married%20later%20in%20life%2C%20unwilling%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20entire%20lives%20to%20their%20jobs%2C%20and%20struggling%20to%20buy%20property.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zurine%20Lau%20Hong%20Kong%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65015d451afe8f0019e94d04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZurine%20Lau%2C%2029%2C%20lives%20with%20her%20parents%20and%20brother.%3Cp%3EZurine%20Lau%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStrikingly%2C%20several%20Hong%20Kong%20millennials%20said%20they%20feel%20different%20from%20Hong%20Kong's%20older%20generations.%20Shin%2C%20the%20fitness%20instructor%2C%20said%20he%20has%20very%20%26quot%3Btraditional%20Chinese%20parents.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20me%20to%20do%20a%20'nicer'%20job%20such%20as%20an%20office%20job%2C%20but%20I%20never%20listen%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong%20millennials%20struggle%20to%20prioritize%20well-being%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20run%20by%20British%20health%20insurance%20company%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bupa.com.hk%2Fen%2Fmedia-centre%2F20230116%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBupa%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20study%20surveyed%20500%20millennials%20aged%2025%20to%2040%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20between%20July%20and%20August%202022.%20It%20found%20that%20the%20generation's%20top%20three%20goals%20are%20sleeping%2C%20exercising%2C%20and%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle.%20However%2C%20for%20many%2C%20those%20goals%20are%20a%20pipe%20dream%3A%20Over%20half%20of%20those%20surveyed%20said%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20time%20to%20maintain%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHong%20Kong%20is%20changing%20in%20so%20many%20ways%20and%20on%20various%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Lau%2C%20the%20account%20manager%20at%20a%20public%20relations%20firm%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20longing%20for%20a%20big%20change%20in%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20why%20I%20want%20to%20live%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20will%20never%20change%20here%20is%20the%20fast%20pace%20of%20life.%20This%20might%20be%20the%20reason%20millennials%20didn't%20want%20to%20stick%20around%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20Lau%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Ng%20is%20happy%20to%20call%20this%20place%20home%2C%20despite%20the%20high%20prices.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20stay%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20I%20am%20a%20native%20of%20Hong%20Kong.%20Most%20of%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20live%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20If%20I%20live%20abroad%2C%20I%20will%20not%20be%20used%20to%20it.%20Hong%20Kong%20is%20a%20very%20convenient%20city.%20No%20matter%20the%20transportation%20or%20the%20food%2C%20it%20is%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20called%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fmillennial-world%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMillennial%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20seeks%20to%20examine%20the%20state%20of%20the%20generation%20around%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhong-kong-millennial-housing-prices-income-debt-dreams-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695003930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65025ccb1afe8f0019ea0f2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhong-kong-millennial-housing-prices-income-debt-dreams-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Millennials%20are%20the%20last%20generation%20born%20before%20the%20July%201%2C%201997%2C%20handover%20of%20Hong%20Kong%20from%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20to%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Faye%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22