Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20UAW%20union%20late%20last%20week%20went%20on%20strike%20to%20pressure%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Three%26quot%3B%20to%20raise%20worker%20wages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strength%20of%20President%20Biden's%20economic%20message%20could%20hinge%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBiden%20has%20sought%20to%20sharpen%20his%202024%20economic%20pitch%2C%20but%20voters%20aren't%20fully%20sold%20on%20his%20message.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20launched%20his%202020%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20his%20first%20major%20rally%20was%20held%20at%20a%20Teamsters%20union%20hall%20in%20Pittsburgh%2C%20where%20he%20extolled%20the%20virtues%20of%20middle-class%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bunion%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.c-span.org%2Fvideo%2F%3F460193-1%2Fjoe-biden-campaign-rally-pittsburgh%5C%22%3Emapped%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20vision%20of%20an%20economy%20that%20would%20empower%20ordinary%20citizens%20by%20lifting%20wages%20and%20targeting%20financial%20loopholes%20that%20favored%20big%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20country%20wasn't%20built%20by%20Wall%20Street%20bankers%2C%20CEOs%2C%20and%20hedge-fund%20managers.%20It%20was%20built%20by%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20receptive%20audience%20in%20April%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20over%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20is%20now%20sitting%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-gm-stellantis-uaw-workers-indefinite-strike-2023-9%5C%22%3Ethe%20United%20Auto%20Workers%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20giving%20him%20the%20most%20challenging%20labor%20crisis%20of%20his%20presidency%2C%20as%20the%20economic%20pitch%20for%20his%20reelection%20bid%20could%20sink%20or%20swim%20depending%20on%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAW%2C%20which%20represents