avily-defended%20cities%20in%20the%20world%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmil.ru%2Ffiles%2Ffiles%2Fpvo100%2Fpage80286.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20air-defense%20district%3C%2Fa%3E%20dating%20back%20to%20Russia's%20civil%20war%20in%201918.%20Thirty-six%20anti-aircraft%20guns%20were%20brought%20into%20defend%20the%20city%20from%20attacks%20by%20counter-revolutionary%20biplanes%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20a%20century%20of%20preparation%20since%2C%20with%20huge%20upgrades%20in%20WWII%20and%20the%20Cold%20War.%20So%20why%20all%20the%20sudden%20activity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBallistic%20defenders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soviet%20Russia%20Moscow%20Red%20Square%20ICBM%20missile%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65075a09cd637c0019c68c3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221652%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20ICBM%20in%20Red%20Square%20during%20a%20military%20parade%20on%20May%2012%2C%201965.%3Cp%3ECentral%20Press%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20appreciate%20just%20how%20extensive%20Moscow's%20air%20defenses%20are%2C%20we%20need%20to%20visit%20the%20suburb%20of%20Filatov%20Lug.%20Sixteen%20miles%20out%20from%20the%20Kremlin%2C%20away%20from%20the%20city%20smoke%2C%20Filatov%20Lug%20boasts%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tripadvisor.com.sg%2FAttraction_Review-g298484-d23592706-Reviews-Filatov_Lug_Park-Moscow_Central_Russia.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20park%20popular%20for%20winter%20skiing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20summer%20amenities%20as%20playgrounds%2C%20picnic%20areas%20and%20walking%20paths%20lined%20with%20wooden%20animal%20sculptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20area%20sealed%20off%20behind%20high%20walls%20contains%20a%20more