tributable%20to%20Neanderthal%20ancestry%20were%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20experience%20severe%20symptoms%20requiring%20hospitalization%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fhealth%2Fwellness%2Fneanderthal-genes-are-linked-to-severe-covid-risk-d992ccad%5C%22%3Ereported%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriting%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fiscience%2Ffulltext%2FS2589-0042(23)01706-6%5C%22%3EiScience%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20researchers%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20nonprofit%20Mario%20Negri%20Institute%20for%20Pharmacological%20Research%2C%20reported%20that%20they%20examined%20the%20DNA%20of%20nearly%201%2C200%20volunteers%20in%20the%20Bergamo%20province%2C%20which%20was%20especially%20hard%20hit%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20What%20they%20found%20is%20that%20%26quot%3BNeanderthal%20haplotype%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20set%20of%20genetic%20variants%20associated%20with%20the%20human%20ancestor%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20major%20genetic%20risk%20factor%20for%20severe%20COVID-19.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20they%20found%20that%20people%20with%20the%20Neanderthal%20haplotype%20were%20twice%20as%20likely%20to%20develop%20severe%20pneumonia%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported%2C%20and%20three%20times%20as%20likely%20to%20end%20up%20on%20a%20ventilator%20in%20an%20intensive-care%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20link%20between%20health%20and%20Neanderthal%20DNA%20has%20been%20suggested%20by%20other%20studies.%20A%20study%20published%20in%20June%20by%20the%20journal%20Molecular%20Biology%20and%20Evolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-interbreeding-between-humans-and-neanderthals-affects-our-health-today-2023-6%5C%22%3Eindicated%20a%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Neanderthal%20DNA%20and%20a%20genetic%20disorder%20known%20as%20Dupuytren's%20disease.%20And%20in%20March%2C%20a%20study%20published%20in%20Nature%20also%20found%20a%20connection%20between%20Neanderthal%20ancestry%20and%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20an%20extreme%20immune%20response%2C%20or%20cytokine%20storm%2C%20from%20contracting%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20news%20tip%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acdavis%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecdavis%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneanderthal-genes-linked-to-severe-cases-of-covid-19-coronavirus-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694963076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e4ea00ba27fc5564e2dfd22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneanderthal-genes-linked-to-severe-cases-of-covid-19-coronavirus-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Research%20by%20scientists%20in%20Italy%20indicates%20that%20people%20with%20gene%20variations%20attributable%20to%20Neanderthal%20ancestry%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20hospitalized.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Charles%20R.%20Davis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A172%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneanderthal-genes-linked-to-severe-cases-of-covid-19-coronavirus-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mason%20Greenwood%20reportedly%20faces%20'die'%20chants%20as%20he%20makes%20Spanish%20league%20debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694959380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-mason-greenwood-getafe_6288485.jpg%3F20230917154629%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmason-greenwood-reportedly-faces-die-chants-as-he-makes-spanish-league-debut-for-getafe-12963611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mason%20Greenwood%20has%20played%20his%20first%20professional%20football%20for%