e%20completely%20destroyed%20in%20last%20week's%20catastrophic%20flooding%2C%20officials%20have%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flibya-flood-damage-revealed-as-10-000-remain-missing-12963520%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flibya-flood-damage-revealed-as-10-000-remain-missing-12963520%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flibya-flood-damage-revealed-as-10-000-remain-missing-12963520%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Just%20Announcing%20Good%20Intentions%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Lead%20India%20into%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20her%20budget%20speech%20on%20February%201%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%202022%2C%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitaraman%20repeatedly%20referred%20to%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20marking%20Azadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%20and%20have%20entered%20into%20Amrit%20Kaal%2C%20the%2025-year-long%20lead%20up%20to%20India%40100%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20was%20first%20used%20by%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20his%20speech%20from%20the%20Red%20Fort%20on%20August%2015%2C%202021%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Independence%20day.%20Elaborating%20on%20the%20concept%2C%20the%20he%20had%20said%20that%20Amrit%20Kaal%20aimed%20to%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20lessen%20the%20divide%20in%20development%20between%20villages%20and%20cities%2C%20reduce%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20interference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20and%20welcome%20the%20latest%20technology.%C2%A0%20Modi%20further%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CStarting%20from%20here%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20next%2025%20years%20is%20the%20Amrit%20Kaal%20of%20a%20new%20India.%20The%20fulfilment%20of%20our%20resolutions%20in%20this%20Amrit%20Kaal%20will%20take%20us%20till%20100%20years%20of%20independence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMilton%20Friedman%2C%20the%20famous%20economist%2C%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20great%20mistakes%20is%20to%20judge%20policies%20and%20programs%20by%20their%20intention%20rather%20than%20their%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20the%20intent%20of%20what%20the%20prime%20minster%20has%20said%20is%20noble.%20However%2C%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20assessed%20is%20whether%20these%20intents%20are%20achievable%3F%20What%20are%20the%20accentuating%20factors%20that%20may%20impede%20achievement%20of%20the%20aim%20and%20how%20to%20overcome%20those%20impediments%3F%20Another%20factor%20that%20we%20have%20to%20consider%20is%20the%20record%20of%20delivery%20of%20the%20assurances%20made%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%209%20years%20don%E2%80%99t%20inspire%20confidence.%20Even%20if%20the%20promises%20of%20recovering%20black%20money%20and%20depositing%20Rs%2015%20lakhs%20in%20bank%20account%20of%20everyone%20are%20considered%20flippancy%2C%20there%20are%20many%20other%20promises%20like%20reigning%20in%20inflation%2C%20reduction%20of%20prices%20of%20LPG%20and%20fuel%2C%20strengthening%20of%20Rupee%20against%20Dollar%2C%20reducing%20poverty%2C%20doubling%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20income%20by%202022%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ehar%20ghar%20nal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20many%20more%20remain%20unrealised.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20we%20now%20have%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20of%20world%2C%20we%20remain%20way%20down%20in%20the%20list%20in%20regard%20to%20per%20capita%20income.%20The%20government%20itself%20admits%20that%20they%20are%20compelled%20to%20give%20subsistence%20ration%20of%20five%20kgs%20every%20month%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20almost%2080%20crore%20people.%20The%20fact%20that%20these%20promises%20could%20not%20be%20fulfilled%20indicates%20that%20the%20planners%20failed%20to%20take%20such%20variables%20into%20account%20which%20may%20have%20adversely%20impacted%20achievement%20of%20those%20objectives.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20some%20of%20the%20factors%20were%20totally%20unexpected%2C%20like%20the%20prolonged%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20However%2C%20some%20other%20causative%20factors%20were%20self-inflicted%2C%20like%20the%20ill-conceived%20demonetisation%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leaders%20therefore%20have%20to%20consider%20all%20factors%20and%20prepare%20tangible%20action%20plans%20to%20overcome%20these%20impediments%20if%20India%20is%20to%20celebrate%20100%20years%20of%20independence%20as%20a%20progressive%20and%20prosperous%20nation%20in%202047.%20Mere%20pronouncement%20of%20intent%20isn%E2%80%99t%20adequate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20founding%20fathers%20laid%20such%20strong%20foundations%20that%20the%20nation%20progressed%20in%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20in%20last%2076%20years.%20During%20this%20period%20our%20economy%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20Tremendous%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20in%20creation%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20industrial%20production%20and%20the%20service%20sector.%20Our%20IITs%20and%20IIMs%20are%20rated%20amongst%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20and%20have%20produced%20many%20bright%20individuals%20who%20have%20excelled%20not%20only%20at%20the%20national%20level%20but%20also%20internationally.%20Several%20alumni%20of%20these%20institutions%20are%20heading%20important%20world%20institutions%20including%20the%20IMF.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjournalism-in-modis-amrit-kaal-is-risky-business%5C%22%3E%20Journalism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20Is%20Risky%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20India%20achieved%20all%20this%20in-spite%20of%20many%20external%20aggressions%20from%20two%20of%20our%20neighbours%20during%20these%20years%20speaks%20for%20the%20strength%20and%20resilience%20of%20our%20economy%20and%20national%20will.%20Our%20political%20and%20military%20leadership%20displayed%20their%20resolve%20by%20facing%C2%A0%20these%20aggressions%20and%20coming%20out%20with%20flying%20colours.%20Several%20insurgencies%20in%20the%20North%20East%20have%20been%20resolved%20amicably%20by%20a%20mix%20of%20security%20and%20population%20centric%20measures%20except%20for%20Manipur%20which%20has%20witnessed%20large%20scale%20ethnic%20violence%20for%20over%20four%20months.%20The%20Maoist%20insurgency%20in%20central%20India%20continues%20to%20rage%20even%20though%20the%20level%20of%20violence%20has%20drastically%20reduced.%20That%20there%20have%20been%20some%20hits%20and%20misses%20is%20only%20natural%20because%20of%20the%20vastness%20and%20diversity%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20tendency%20of%20humans%20to%20repeat%20the%20success%20of%20their%20last%20endeavour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20should%20not%20be%20difficult%20for%20the%20present%20and%20future%20leadership%20of%20India%20to%20take%20the%20nation%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20India%20stands%20at%20the%20front%20of%20comity%20of%20nations.%20However%2C%20for%20this%20to%20happen%20the%20leadership%20has%20to%20be%20forward%20thinking%20and%20formulate%20policies%20after%20war%20gaming%20futuristic%20scenarios.%20Such%20policies%20must%20conform%20to%20the%20changing%20environment%20and%20demands%20of%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeace%20and%20tranquility%20is%20the%20first%20requisite%20for%20realising%20the%20potential%20of%20India%20to%20become%20a%20leading%20world%20power.%20Several%20fault%20lines%20in%20our%20society%20which%20put%20heavy%20strain%20on%20our%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20our%20destiny%20must%20be%20addressed%20urgently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20major%20fault%20line%20that%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20is%20the%20increasing%20communalisation%20of%20our%20society.%20Besides%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3Eriots%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fthe-manipur-crisis-in-numbers-four-months-of-unending-violence%5C%22%3EManipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20cases%20of%20mob%20violence%20which%20are%20directly%20attributed%20to%20increasing%20radicalisation%20amongst%20masses.%20Religious%20processions%20with%20crowds%20carrying%20weapons%20while%20shouting%20provocative%20slogans%20end%20up%20disturbing%20peace%20and%20result%20in%20violence.%20Terms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Clove%20jihad%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fneo-khalistanis-cow-vigilantes-challenge-indias-security-establishment%5C%22%3Ecow%20vigilantism%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20are%20now%20in%20common%20lexicon.%20People%20involved%20in%20traditional%20cattle%20trade%20are%20wantonly%20attacked%20by%20alleging%20that%20the%20animals%20are%20being%20carried%20for%20slaughter.%20There%20are%20instances%20of%20people%20having%20been%20killed%20on%20mere%20suspicion%20meat%20in%20their%20fridge%20being%20beef!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ethnic%20strife%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20inability%20of%20the%20government%20to%20contain%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20and%20may%20fuel%20secessionist%20tendencies%20in%20the%20North-East%20once%20again.%20The%20leaders%20must%20behave%20in%20statesman-like%20manner%20and%20rise%20above%20the%20parochial%20considerations%20of%20religion%2C%20ethnicity%20and%20language.%20The%20leaders%20must%20work%20towards%20emotional%20integration%20of%20people%20from%20all%20regions%2C%20religions%20and%20ethnicity.%20The%20grievances%20of%20people%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20North-East%20and%20Tribal%20areas%20in%20central%20India%20must%20be%20addressed%20for%20ensuring%20peace%20which%20is%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20progress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20now%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20of%20the%20world%20leaving%20China%20behind.%20More%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20is%20below%20the%20age%20of%2025%20years%20and%20more%20than%2065%25%20below%20the%20age%20of%2035.%20However%2C%20this%20population%20dividend%20will%20prove%20ineffective%20if%20adequate%20employment%20opportunities%20are%20not%20available%20in%20the%20country.%20With%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20hovering%20at%20around%207.5%25%2C%20the%20symptoms%20of%20restiveness%20amongst%20youth%20are%20already%20visible.%20Anecdotal%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20people%20involved%20in%20rioting%20and%20vigilantism%20are%20mostly%20unemployed%20youth.%20Unemployment%20therefore%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%20urgently%20by%20strengthening%20the%20manufacturing%20as%20well%20as%20service%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwho-is-afraid-of-otherness%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20Otherness%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20reason%20often%20cited%20for%20unemployment%20or%20rather%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20employment%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20adequately%20skilled%20man%20power.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20standards%20of%20education%20have%20diluted%20drastically%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20There%20is%20no%20quality%20check%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20resource%20persons%20employed%20in%20the%20educational%20institutions%20which%20have%20mushroomed%20haphazardly%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20We%20are%20therefore%20churning%20out%20under%20qualified%20engineers%2C%20doctors%20and%20MBAs%20from%20establishments%20housed%20in%20one%20or%20two%20rooms%20facility%20without%20any%20laboratories%20or%20other%20essential%20infrastructure.%20These%20establishments%20do%20not%20meet%20the%20stringent%20requirements%20of%20industry%20yet%20manage%20to%20obtain%20approval%20%E2%80%93%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20obtained%20through%20underhand%20means.%20Such%20people%20are%20thus%20compelled%20to%20take%20up%20jobs%20which%20are%20way%20below%20their%20%E2%80%9Cqualification%20on%20paper%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20dissatisfaction.%20Educational%20institutions%20must%20therefore%20be%20subjected%20to%20strict%20quality%20control%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20resource%20persons%20and%20quality%20and%20content%20of%20education%20imparted.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20must%20also%20focus%20on%20improving%20primary%20education%20in%20far%20flung%20remote%20areas%20and%20villages.%20The%20government%20schools%20in%20villages%20are%20the%20most%20neglected.%20It%20is%20utopian%20to%20expect%20such%20schools%20to%20have%20any%20other%20facility%20essential%20for%20all-round%20personality%20development%20of%20a%20child.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20area%20where%20India%20needs%20to%20focus%20is%20the%20health%20infrastructure.%20While%20we%20are%20focusing%20on%20creating%20tertiary%20level%20facilities%20like%20AIIMS%20in%20big%20cities%2C%20we%20are%20not%20creating%20adequate%20primary%20and%20secondary%20level%20facilities%20in%20villages%2C%20and%20small%20cities%2C%20leading%20to%20overcrowding%20in%20the%20city%20hospitals.%20Only%20a%20healthy%20population%20can%20gainfully%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%20and%20expansion%20of%20our%20economy.%20The%20Primary%20health%20centres%20in%20villages%20must%20be%20strengthened.%20All%20those%20graduating%20from%20medical%20colleges%20must%20be%20compelled%20to%20initially%20work%20in%20rural%20areas%20at%20least%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20Adequate%20trained%20staff%20and%20medicines%20must%20also%20be%20made%20available%20in%20these%20primary%20health%20centres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20but%20not%20the%20least%2C%20the%20government%20must%20provide%20a%20humane%20and%20responsive%20administration%20which%20treats%20the%20citizen%20as%20priority.%20It%20is%20often%20seen%20that%20the%20general%20public%20keeps%20running%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20for%20redressal%20of%20even%20minor%20grievances.%20Most%20of%20the%20government%20functionaries%20and%20even%20elected%20representatives%20do%20not%20treat%20common%20public%20with%20empathy.%20Many%20bureaucrats%20resort%20to%20bribe%20taking%20even%20for%20doing%20something%20which%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20individual.%20Remote%20villages%20are%20hardly%20ever%20visited%20by%20bureaucrats%20and%20such%20places%20never%20ever%20get%20to%20see%20the%20face%20of%20a%20government%20authority.%20The%20elected%20representatives%20too%20do%20not%20visit%20their%20constituencies%20regularly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpolice-uniform-modi%5C%22%3EReform%2C%20Not%20Uniform%3A%20Why%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Plan%20for%20the%20Police%20in%20India%20is%20Totally%20Off%20the%20Mark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20neglect%20leads%20to%20dissatisfaction%20and%20is%20cause%20of%20simmering%20unrest%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20avoidable%20agitations.%20Part%20of%20the%20problem%20lies%20in%20the%20selection%20process%20of%20the%20leaders%20heading%20the%20bureaucracy.%20Selected%20through%20a%20testing%20process%20which%20focusses%20mainly%20on%20rote%20memory%2C%20they%20undergo%20motions%20of%20a%20training%20process%20which%20encourages%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20equip%20them%20to%20interpret%20the%20laws%20of%20land%20with%20empathy%2C%20leading%20to%20plethora%20of%20litigation%20where%20the%20government%20is%20either%20a%20litigant%20or%20a%20respondent.%20Not%20that%20litigation%20for%20a%20common%20man%20is%20easy.%20The%20courts%20take%20years%20to%20decide%20a%20case.%20Even%20matters%20like%20granting%20of%20bail%20are%20decided%20after%20lengthy%20arguments%20and%20several%20postponements.%20The%20lower%20courts%20in%20many%20cases%20are%20happy%20abdicating%20their%20responsibility%20by%20passing%20ambiguous%20orders.%20Besides%20the%20unduly%20long%20time%20taken%2C%20litigation%20is%20very%20costly%20which%20a%20regualr%20person%20cannot%20afford%20especially%20in%20the%20High%20courts%20and%20Supreme%20Court.%20Both%20bureaucracy%20and%20judicial%20systems%20are%20in%20urgent%20need%20of%20reforms%20if%20the%20stated%20aim%20of%20government%20is%20to%20be%20achieved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20July%205%20renamed%20%E2%80%9CAmrit%20Kal%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9CKartavya%20Kal%E2%80%9D%20i.e.%20the%20era%20of%20%E2%80%98duty%E2%80%99%2C%20imploring%20the%20public%20to%20perform%20their%20duties%20diligently%20in%20order%20to%20make%20India%20an%20advanced%20country%20during%20the%20period%20leading%20to%202047.%20The%20emphasis%20thus%20has%20been%20placed%20on%20performance%20of%20duties%20as%20the%20first%20priority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20the%20nation%20cannot%20progress%20without%20every%20citizen%20performing%20their%20duty%20towards%20nation%20building%20diligently.%20However%2C%20reforms%20and%20course%20correction%20suggested%20above%20must%20also%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20government%20to%20realise%20the%20dream%20of%20India%20becoming%20a%20truly%20progressive%20and%20prosperous%20nation.%20Our%20leaders%20must%20display%20the%20sagacity%20to%20address%20the%20fault%20lines%20and%20work%20with%20single%20minded%20devotion%20to%20achieve%20that%20aim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESanjiv%20Krishan%20Sood%20retired%20as%20additional%20director%20general%2C%20Border%20Security%20Force.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694955645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjust-announcing-good-intentions-wont-lead-india-into-amrit-kaal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20cannot%20abdicate%20it's%20responsibilities%20by%20shifting%20the%20onus%20on%20citizens%20to%20perform%20their%20duty%20towards%20nation%20building.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjust-announcing-good-intentions-wont-lead-india-into-amrit-kaal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Looking%20Past%20the%20Government%20Narrative%20Around%20the%20G20%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09162344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-09-at-4.22.17.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20air%20%E2%80%93%20or%20water%3F%20The%20recent%20G20%20summit%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emaya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20which%2C%20in%20the%20later%20Vedic%20texts%2C%20is%20said%20to%20connote%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmagic%20show%2C%20an%20illusion%20where%20things%20appear%20to%20be%20present%20but%20are%20not%20what%20they%20seem%E2%80%9D.%20In%20effect%2C%20%C2%A0the%20same%20thing%20seems%20different%20to%20different%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20evidence%20of%20this%20is%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20passed%20on%20September%2013%2C%20and%20the%20same%20evening%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20BJP%20parliamentary%20party%20at%20the%20party%20headquarters%20which%20was%20dressed%20up%20to%20the%20queens%20to%20felicitate%20its%20leader%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20lavish%20festivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20sentiment%20and%20language%20in%20sycophantic%20exaltation%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20mark%20both%20documents.%20Dripping%20with%20sugary%20praise%2C%20the%20two-page%20BJP%20resolution%20said%20that%20the%20G20%20summit%20%E2%80%9Cstands%20as%20a%20monumental%20chapter%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20annals%2C%20marking%20a%20transformative%20moment%20in%20how%20our%20nation%20is%20perceived%E2%80%A6.on%20the%20global%20stage%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cabinet%20resolution%2C%20moved%20by%20the%20defence%20minister%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20on%20a%20day%20Army%20officers%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%5C%22%3Elaying%20down%20their%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20high-profile%20sensitive%20security%20zone%2C%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Crecognized%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20giving%20the%20Indian%20G20%20Presidency%20a%20strong%20direction%E2%80%A6in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%20The%20resolution%20further%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20outcomes%20of%20the%20Summit%20were%20transformational%20and%20would%20contribute%20to%20the%20reshaping%20of%20the%20global%20order%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBriefing%20the%20media%20on%20the%20cabinet%20resolution%2C%20information%20and%20broadcasting%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20successful%20hosting%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20is%20symbol%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20efficient%20leadership%20and%20strong%20will%20and%20it%20is%20being%20talked%20about%20in%20the%20entire%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeave%20aside%20the%20sheer%20ordinariness%20of%20the%20language%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20street-smart%20young%20politician%20on%20the%20make%20who%20is%20not%20above%20incendiary%20speech-making%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20announced%20here%20is%20the%20clearest%20intent%20to%20milk%20the%20G20%20Summit%20for%20all%20it%20is%20worth%20for%20purposes%20of%20domestic%20propaganda%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%20Connect%20the%20dots%20and%20this%20is%20the%20story%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20artful%20flourish%2C%20in%20this%20atmosphere%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20asked%20the%20assembled%20crowd%20at%20the%20felicitation%20ceremony%20if%20their%20hearts%20didn%E2%80%99t%20swell%20with%20pride%20and%20their%20heads%20weren%E2%80%99t%20held%20a%20little%20higher%20after%20the%20G20%20Summit%20held%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Has%20the%20Indian%20G20%20Presidency%20Addressed%20the%20Global%20South's%20Economic%20Challenges%20and%20Priorities%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhas-the-indian-g20-presidency-addressed-the-global-souths-economic-challenges-and-priorities%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20Indian%20G20%20Presidency%20Addressed%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20Challenges%20and%20Priorities%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20country%2C%20alas%2C%20tragedy%20had%20been%20enacted%20earlier%20the%20same%20day%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Kokernag%20in%20South%20Kashmir%20where%2C%20belying%20repeated%20official%20claims%20that%20terrorism%20had%20been%20beaten%20back%20after%20the%20annulling%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20autonomy%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20colonel%20and%20a%20major%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20and%20a%20deputy%20SP%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20were%20mowed%20down%20by%20terrorists%2C%20casting%20widespread%20gloom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20of%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20colonel%20in%20such%20circumstances%20is%20typically%20deemed%20very%20serious.%20But%20this%20didn%E2%80%99t%20dampen%20the%20mood%20at%20the%20ostentatious%20event%20in%20New%20Delhi%20organised%20to%20praise%20the%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manipulation%20of%20national%20public%20opinion%20to%20imprint%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20mind%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20has%20now%20come%20to%20be%20the%20guide%20of%20the%20world%2C%20not%20only%20the%20country%2C%20and%20that%20its%20leader%20is%20the%20cynosure%20of%20all%20eyes%20in%20any%20international%20setting%2C%20is%20evidently%20the%20reason%20for%20New%20Delhi%20urging%20the%20G20%20forum%20to%20let%20it%20host%20the%20summit%20in%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20rather%20than%20two%20years%20prior%2C%20when%20it%20was%20due%20in%20the%20normal%20course.%20All%20energies%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20then%20bent%20to%20extract%20as%20much%20as%20mileage%20as%20possible%20from%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20a%20consensus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20summit%20of%20the%20G20%20is%20typically%20a%20fairly%20mundane%20affair%20when%20it%20is%20held%20in%20member%20countries%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20There%20is%20no%20fanfare.%20The%20local%20media%20does%20not%20get%20down%20to%20churning%20out%20words%20and%20images%20of%20frenzied%20adulation%2C%20as%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20so-called%20mainstream%20did%20in%20India.%20There%20is%20no%20felicitation%20ceremony%20to%20mark%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20leader.%20Cabinet%20resolutions%20are%20not%20passed%20in%20praise.%20The%20summit%20is%20not%20held%20in%20a%20specially%20constructed%20building%20for%20the%20occasion%2C%20such%20as%20a%20Bharat%20Mandapam%2C%20as%20if%20to%20stamp%20a%20legacy.%20The%20guests%20are%20not%20fed%20in%20silver%20plates%20as%20at%20a%20maharaja%E2%80%99s%20wedding%20reception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20consensus%20document%20that%20emerges%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20deliberations%20summarises%20the%20outcome.%20This%20is%20a%20fairly%20routine%20affair%20since%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20richest%20seven%20countries%2C%20the%20G7%2C%20had%20mooted%20the%20idea%20for%20wider%20consultation%20and%20interaction%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20international%20financial%20stability%20and%20roped%20in%20the%2012%20largest%20economies%20and%20the%20EU%2C%20besides%20themselves%2C%20in%20order%20to%20conduct%20practical%2C%20common%20sense%20discussions%20with%20a%20view%20to%20fixing%20relevant%20targets%20and%20aspirations%20to%20keep%20the%20world%20from%20wobbling%20financially%2C%20as%20had%20happened%20in%202007-8.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20much%20more%20to%20it%20really%20%E2%80%93%20but%20in%20India%20it%20was%20all%20very%20different.%20The%20leadership%20gave%20the%20impression%20that%20it%20was%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20convince%20its%20own%20people%20that%20the%20summit%2C%20fronted%20by%20their%20dear%20leader%2C%20was%20a%20walk%20for%20them%20in%20a%20newly%20laid%20garden%20in%20the%20heavens%2C%20with%20the%20angels%20dancing%20and%20singing%20the%20leader%E2%80%99s%20praise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20warts%20were%20covered%20with%20green%20cloth%20over%20the%20slum%20areas%2C%20traffic%20was%20kept%20off%20the%20roads%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20avoid%20guests%E2%80%99%20exposure%20to%20grime%20and%20dust%2C%20and%20to%20pre-empt%20any%20chance%20of%20a%20surprise%20public%20protest%20sprung%20on%20the%20organisers%20since%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%20has%20regressed%20for%20ordinary%20folk%20for%20long%20in%20the%20Modi%20regime.%20But%20with%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20complicity%2C%20to%20dress%20up%20an%20ordinary%20annual%20international%20happening%20as%20a%20celestial%20event%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20cost%20the%20exchequer%20some%20four%20times%20of%20what%20was%20budgeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20true%20enough%20that%20the%2018th%C2%A0summit%20of%20the%20G20%20in%20New%20Delhi%20became%20an%20unintended%20victim%20of%20the%20East-West%20confrontation%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20The%20G7%20block%2C%20in%20order%20to%20assert%20its%20political%20primacy%2C%20tried%20to%20censure%20Russia%20by%20name%20and%20in%20strong%20language%2C%20as%20it%20has%20done%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20and%20at%20the%20Bali%20G20%20summit%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20round%20the%20same%20approach%20would%20have%20wrecked%20the%20chance%20of%20a%20consensus%20document%20emerging.%20India%20is%20on%20sweet%20terms%20with%20Moscow%20for%20its%20massive%20oil%20supplies%20at%20bewilderingly%20low%20costs%20which%20the%20Indians%20happily%20trade%20with%20the%20Europeans%20at%20market%20prices%2C%20and%20make%20a%20quick%20buck%20as%20middlemen.%20New%20Delhi%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20put%20Moscow%20through%20humiliation%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20western%20powers.%20There%20are%20other%20geopolitical%20considerations%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Five%20Keys%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffive-keys-takeaways-from-the-g20-summit-in-delhi%5C%22%3EFive%20Keys%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20thus%20in%20a%20bind%20%E2%80%93%20the%20prospect%20of%20embarrassment%20made%20worse%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20decided%20to%20not%20attend%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20the%20Indian%20hosts%20look%20small%2C%20and%20also%20to%20calibrate%20China%E2%80%99s%20position%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20US%20whose%20leader%20was%20hoping%20to%20meet%20Xi%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20a%20conversation%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20Big-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20of%20all%20people%20the%20Americans%20and%20their%20European%20allies%20came%20to%20the%20rescue.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20India%20has%20bought%20massive%20amounts%20of%20military%20equipment%20from%20the%20US%20and%20France%2C%20and%20there%20is%20always%20the%20prospect%20of%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20most%20significant%20two-way%20meeting%20in%20the%20two%20days%20the%20world%20leaders%20were%20in%20Delhi%2C%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20bilateral%20with%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20outcome%20was%20an%20agreement%20on%20more%20variegated%20military%20supplies%20%E2%80%93%20with%20India%20probably%20also%20agreeing%20to%20offer%20the%20US%20a%20military%20base%2C%20as%20may%20be%20read%20in%20the%20reported%20language%20of%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20lubricant%20provided%20by%20luscious%20levels%20of%20trade%20in%20defence%20hardware%2C%20prudence%20dictated%20that%20the%20G7%20block%20do%20not%20push%20India%20hard%20on%20the%20Russia%20question.%20The%20US%20also%20has%20in%20mind%20that%20India%20is%20on%20its%20side%20in%20the%20strategic%20confrontation%20of%20the%20age%20with%20China.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20service%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20others%2C%20gave%20an%20excellent%20account%20of%20themselves%20in%20handling%20the%20rigours%20of%20the%20rituals%20of%20diplomacy%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20was%20down%20to%20the%20bare%20knuckles.%20Being%20from%20this%20brood%2C%20the%20energetic%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20knows%20his%20onions.%20Amitabh%20Kant%2C%20a%20retired%20administrator%20of%20diverse%20experience%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20point%20man%20for%20G20%2C%20also%20appears%20to%20have%20learnt%20the%20tricks%20of%20the%20trade%20in%20holding%20his%20ground%20with%20international%20negotiators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%2C%20really%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20thing%2C%20though.%20When%20all%20is%20said%2C%20was%20the%20G20%20Summit%20an%20international%20event%20being%20held%20this%20year%20in%20India%20as%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20part%20of%20a%20rotational%20annual%20exercise%2C%20or%20was%20it%20at%20the%20primary%20level%20a%20domestic%20event%20planned%20and%20executed%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20politics%3F%20If%20%E2%80%9Cmaya%E2%80%9D%20of%20our%20ancient%20texts%20is%20something%20that%20is%20present%20but%20is%20not%20what%20it%20appears%20to%20be%2C%20then%20the%20%C2%A0summit%20fits%20that%20description.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20political%20dynamics%20in%20the%20three%20north%20Indian%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20headed%20for%20elections%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months%20are%20widely%20reported%20to%20be%20discouraging%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Should%20Modi%20think%20to%20bring%20on%20the%20national%20election%20as%20well%20alongside%2C%20in%20order%20to%20lift%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20chances%20as%20he%20campaigns%20simultaneously%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20polls%20in%20these%20and%20two%20other%20states%2C%20then%20the%20G20%20summit%20%E2%80%93%20at%20which%20he%20played%20the%20showman%20%E2%80%93%20may%20be%20the%20perfect%20foil%20to%20opposition%20ingresses%20which%20are%20running%20up%20a%20political%20scare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%3Cem%3EAlexandria%20Quartet%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lawrence%20Durrell%20retells%20the%20same%20story%20in%20different%20volumes%20but%20from%20the%20standpoint%20of%20different%20characters.%20The%20G20%20Summit%20is%20the%20Modi%20narration.%20But%20there%20is%20also%20another%20narrative%2C%20a%20very%20different%20one%2C%20waiting%20to%20come%20out.%20When%20the%20story%20of%20ordinary%20people%2C%20on%20whose%20living%20conditions%20a%20green%20%3Cem%3Epurdah%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20thrown%20so%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20boasts%20of%20development%20are%20not%20exposed%20as%20dubious%2C%20bursts%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20the%20manicured%20image%20of%20the%20rulers%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20rudely%20disturbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20for%20two%20days%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20a%20life%20of%20shocking%20extravagance%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20guests%20by%20Modi%20and%20his%20team%20in%20the%20style%20of%20medieval-era%20feudal%20lords%20feting%20a%20favoured%20child%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ebaraat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20bridegroom%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20this%20country%E2%80%99s%20economic%20metrics%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20just%20as%20shocking.%20For%20GDP%20per%20capita%2C%20or%20the%20income%20available%20per%20head%20of%20population%2C%20roughly%20speaking%2C%20India%20stands%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20list%20of%20G20%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20count%20of%20the%20Human%20Development%20Index%2C%20which%20measures%20life%20expectancy%2C%20education%20and%20standard%20of%20living%2C%20every%20G20%20nation%20is%20ahead%20of%20India.%20The%20data%2C%20featured%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20%3C%2Fem%3Earticle%2C%20is%20collated%20from%20the%20World%20Bank%20Open%20Data%20and%20Our%20World%20in%20Data%2C%20by%20Rebecca%20Rose%20Varghese.%20With%20figures%20such%20as%20these%2C%20what%20aid%20to%20poorer%20countries%20can%20India%20offer%20on%20any%20viable%20basis%3F%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20crass%20propaganda%20is%20that%20the%20world%20is%20falling%20at%20our%20feet%20on%20account%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20other%20G20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20leaders%20insist%20India%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20poorer%20sections%20of%20the%20world%20community%2C%20nowadays%20more%20commonly%20called%20the%20Global%20South.%20Some%2070%25%20of%20the%20world%20today%20labours%20under%20an%20enormous%20debt%20burden%20on%20account%20of%20structural%20problems%20exacerbated%20by%20severe%20economic%20stoppages%20and%20collapse%20in%20the%20Covid%20period.%20India%20is%20also%20yet%20to%20regain%20the%20pre-Covid%20levels%20of%20economic%20activity%20and%20earnings.%20Its%20labouring%20classes%2C%20and%20those%20in%20the%20small%20and%20medium%20industry%2C%20including%20their%20owners%2C%20who%20make%20up%20a%20very%20high%20proportion%20of%20our%20population%2C%20are%20the%20most%20seriously%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Modi%20has%20crowned%20himself%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20pride%20of%20India%2C%20who%20made%20the%20summit%20happen%20at%20a%20moment%20of%20his%20choosing%2C%20and%20cast%20the%20event%20in%20his%20own%20likeness%2C%20he%20should%20answer%20why%20such%20a%20massive%20splurge%20of%20the%20taxpayers%E2%80%99%20money%20was%20necessary.%20He%20would%20be%20hard%20put%20to%20say%20anything%20that%20makes%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133601%2F5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133601%2F5.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133601%2F5-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133601%2F5-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672092%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Coolie%20Camp%20area%20was%20covered%20with%20a%20green%20curtain%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20concealing%20the%20houses%20within.%20Photo%3A%20Atul%20Ashok%20Howale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPossibly%20the%20most%20striking%20aspect%20of%20the%20summit%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye%20was%20the%20shoving%20aside%20of%20the%20local%20and%20the%20world%20media.%20Even%20the%20typically%20combative%20US%20press%20corps%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20its%20own%20president.%20It%20was%20kept%20shuttered%20in%20its%20cage.%20President%20Biden%20too%20came%20under%20curfew%20rules%20%E2%80%93%20no%20interaction%20with%20the%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20pathetic%20sight%20%E2%80%93%20and%20no%20advertisement%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20US%20leader%20was%20able%20to%20hold%20his%20first%20press%20conference%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20summit%20he%20had%20just%20left%20behind%20only%20after%20arriving%20in%20Vietnam%20from%20New%20Delhi.%20And%20yet%2C%20there%20was%20a%20parting%20gift%20for%20foreign%20guests.%20They%20were%20presented%20a%20book%20of%20dubious%20information%20but%20nice%20pictures%2C%20purporting%20to%20show%20that%20India%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9CMother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%9D%20from%20ancient%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20pity-inducing%20circumstance%20in%20Modi%20Raj%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98People%E2%80%99s-20%20summit%E2%80%99%20was%20also%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%20about%20a%20fortnight%20before%20the%20G20%20event%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20dire%20conditions%20of%20life%20for%20the%20many.%20It%20received%20rough%20treatment%20from%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportant%20participants-%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20politicians%2C%20civil%20society%20activists%20and%20senior%20professionals%20from%20different%20fields%20%E2%80%93%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-delhi-police-jairam-ramesh-leaders%5C%22%3Estopped%20from%20entering%20the%20venue%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20grounds%20of%20a%20flimsy%20technicality.%20And%20those%20who%20managed%20to%20gain%20entry%20were%20not%20being%20allowed%20out%2C%20as%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20found%20to%20his%20dismay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disregard%20for%20the%20lives%20of%20others%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20those%20not%20in%20the%20strawberry%20and%20cream%20bracket%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20arm-twisting%20of%20the%20media%20lest%20the%20reality%20come%20tumbling%20out%2C%20make%20up%20an%20important%20aspect%20of%20the%20lives%20we%20lead%20in%20India.%20Thus%2C%20coinciding%20roughly%20with%20the%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20meet%2C%20New%20Delhi%20also%20staged%20a%20media%20conclave%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fm20%5C%22%3Ethe%20M20%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20a%20first%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20international%20summitry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20there%20is%20something%20to%20be%20said%20for%20India%2C%20after%20all.%20A%20bubbling%20up%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20sentiment%20is%20a%20prospect%20which%20is%20always%20only%20a%20step%20away%20from%20the%20surface.%20This%20makes%20the%20rulers%20wary%20though%20they%20have%20an%20impressive%20line%20of%20ardent%20supporters%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20of%20the%20US%20and%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20of%20France.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20too%20worshipful%20media%20at%20home.%20One%20of%20these%20has%20just%20proclaimed%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20ratings%20have%20soared%20after%20G20.%20Sound%20familiar%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20journalist%20and%20political%20commentator%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694953823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09162344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-09-at-4.22.17.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flooking-past-the-government-narrative-around-the-g20-summit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20government%20has%20shown%20clearest%20intent%20to%20milk%20the%20G20%20Summit%20for%20all%20it%20is%20worth%20for%20purposes%20of%20domestic%20propaganda%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flooking-past-the-government-narrative-around-the-g20-summit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Organisational%20Unity%20of%20%E2%80%98Utmost%20Importance%E2%80%99%20Says%20Kharge%20as%20Congress%20Chalks%20Out%20Poll%20Strategy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17172550%2FF6NXWAsXUAAXN2b.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EOn%20day%20two%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Telangana%2C%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20stressed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20organisational%20unity%20ahead%20of%20key%20state%20elections%20and%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20and%20urged%20party%20leaders%20to%20%E2%80%9Cavoid%20going%20to%20the%20media%20with%20statements%20against%20leaders%20or%20the%20party%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20meeting%20which%20concluded%20on%20Sunday%20(September%2017)%20was%20the%20first%20conducted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcong-appoints-new-working-committee-ahead-of-elections%5C%22%3Enew%20CWC%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20includes%2039%20main%20members%2C%20who%20were%20appointed%20by%20Kharge%20in%20August.%20It%20also%20has%20special%20invitees%2C%20ex-officio%20members%20and%20incharges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20one%20the%20party%20in%20its%20resolution%20called%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-calls-for-increasing-upper-limit-on-reservations-at-historic-cwc-meeting%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20the%20upper%20limit%20on%20reservations%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Castes%20(OBC)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20probe%20into%20the%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20allegations%20against%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20businesses%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20demand%20to%20bring%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20bill%20in%20the%20upcoming%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20extended%20CWC%20meeting%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20party%20focused%20on%20organisational%20issues%20and%20poll%20preparations%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20and%20the%20general%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrganisational%20unity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20remarks%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Corganisational%20unity%E2%80%9D%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20as%20the%20party%20prepares%20for%20the%20key%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20These%20challenges%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20those%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%3B%20they%20concern%20the%20survival%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20the%20preservation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20recent%20victories%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20have%20proved%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%9Care%20looking%20for%20an%20alternative%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20work%20tirelessly%2C%20putting%20aside%20personal%20interests.%20We%20must%20prioritise%20the%20success%20of%20the%20party%20putting%20aside%20our%20personal%20differences.%20We%20must%20exercise%20self-restraint%20and%20avoid%20going%20to%20media%20with%20statements%20against%20our%20leaders%20or%20party.%20So%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20interests%20are%20not%20harmed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20the%20party%20leaders%20present%20to%20ensure%20that%20confidentiality%20is%20maintained%20about%20the%20strategies%20being%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLikewise%2C%20organisational%20unity%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance.%20Only%20through%20unity%20and%20discipline%20can%20we%20defeat%20our%20adversaries.%20This%20was%20evident%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20we%20remained%20united%20and%20fought%20with%20discipline%20to%20achieve%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202014%2C%20the%20party%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20series%20of%20desertions%2C%20with%20many%20top%20leaders%20leaving%20the%20party%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20along%20with%20factionalism%20in%20regional%20units%2C%20as%20well%20as%20internal%20rivalries%20that%20impeded%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-congress-president%5C%22%3E%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20elevation%20to%20the%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20party%20has%20won%20two%20state%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20larger%2026-party%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%20should%20not%20only%20prepare%20for%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections%20that%20are%20scheduled%20but%20also%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20state%20presidents%20and%20legislative%20party%20leaders%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%20whether%20local%20committees%20at%20the%20block%2C%20mandal%20and%20district%20level%20are%20ready%2C%20the%20regular%20programmes%20being%20prepared%20and%20whether%20potential%20candidates%20have%20been%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20social%20justice%20and%20welfarism%20schemes%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20governments%20need%20to%20be%20publicised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C..We%20cannot%20remain%20mute%20spectators.%20We%20must%20unite%20and%20overthrow%20this%20dictatorial%20government%20in%20order%20to%20save%20our%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20resolution%20passed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20extended%20CWC%20meeting%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20party%20said%20that%20it%20had%20reaffirmed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpreparedness%20of%20the%20party%20organisation%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20concluding%20remarks%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20preparedness%20for%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20organisational%20unity%2C%20he%20said%20that%20if%20there%20are%20differences%20they%20need%20to%20be%20sorted%20out%20by%20the%20leadership%20at%20the%20local%20and%20central%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouth%20outreach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20party%20also%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20young%20voters%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20voters%20between%2018%20and%2025%20years%20of%20age.%20We%20have%20to%20tell%20them%20about%20our%20ideology%2C%20about%20our%20history%20and%20about%20our%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kharge%20in%20his%20closing%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20prepare%20an%20army%20of%20young%20speakers%20who%20will%20convey%20the%20ideology%20of%20our%20party%20to%20the%20youth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20is%20also%20holding%20a%20rally%20in%20Tukkuguda%20near%20Hyderabad%20on%20Sunday%20as%20the%20state%20celebrates%20Telangana%20National%20Integration%20Day%20which%20marks%20the%20day%20on%20which%20the%20princely%20State%20of%20Hyderabad%20merged%20with%20the%20Indian%20Union%20in%201948.%3C%