%2Farticle67312174.ece%5C%22%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Social%20Justice%20and%20Empowerment%20has%20justified%20the%20move%20by%20questioning%20the%20%E2%80%9Cquality%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20socio-economic%20data%20collected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInformation%20on%20categories%20like%20caste%2C%20level%20of%20education%2C%20employment%20status%2C%20income%20(personal%20and%20family)%20and%20marital%20status%20of%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20has%20been%20shelved%20with%20officials%20saying%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20form%20was%20always%20to%20collect%20disability%20data%20and%20hence%20all%20other%20fields%20were%20made%20optional%20which%20led%20to%20many%20skipping%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajesh%20Aggarwal%2C%20Secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Empowerment%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(DEPwD)%20of%20the%20Social%20Justice%20Ministry%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20are%20not%20being%20released%20because%20of%20quality%20issues.%E2%80%9D%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20department%20intends%20to%20pursue%20collecting%20socio-economic%20data%20for%20future%20UDID%20registrations%2C%20Aggarwal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovt-shelves-socio-economic-data-of-pwds-as-disability-database-goes-online%2Farticle67312174.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20purpose%20of%20the%20form%20is%20to%20get%20a%20disability%20certificate%E2%80%A6%20and%20also%2C%20we%20cannot%20afford%20to%20make%20the%20form%20too%20lengthy%20by%20seeking%20information%20we%20cannot%20verify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DEPwD%20earlier%20this%20week%20published%20what%20it%20called%20aggregated%20data%20from%20the%20around%2094%20lakh%20UDID%20registrations%2C%20minus%20the%20socio-economic%20data%2C%20with%20a%20statement%20alongside%20spelling%20out%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20project%20%E2%80%93%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20a%20national%20database%20for%20all%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(PwDs)%20along%20with%20their%20socio-economic%20details%E2%80%9D%20so%20that%20policy-making%20and%20interventions%20can%20be%20targeted%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20not%20officially%20disclosed%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20people%20who%20filled%20in%20the%20socio-economic%20fields.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funion-government-defends-decision-to-remove-questions-on-disability-from-nfhs-6%5C%22%3EUnion%20Government%20Defends%20Decision%20to%20Remove%20Questions%20on%20Disability%20From%20NFHS-6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20heads%20under%20which%20the%20government%20chose%20not%20to%20publish%20data%20are%20the%20fields%20of%20personal%20and%20family%20income%20(spouse%20and%20father)%2C%20whether%20they%20were%20Below%20Poverty%20Line%2C%20employment%20status%2C%20occupation%2C%20socio-economic%20category%20(SC%2FST%2FOBC%2FGeneral)%2C%20and%20level%20of%20education.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20government%20official%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20marital%20status%20%E2%80%93%20only%20about%2015%25%20of%20those%20registered%20have%20filled%20it%20in.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20data%20to%20be%20significant.%20Again%2C%20information%20on%20income%2C%20just%2040%25%20have%20filled%20it%20in.%20The%20department%20has%20no%20way%20to%20verify%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20information%20is%20accurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20official%20aware%20of%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20enough%E2%80%9D%20people%20had%20responded%20to%20fields%20such%20as%20education%20and%20socio-economic%20category%20either%2C%20adding%20this%20was%20among%20the%20primary%20reasons%20for%20discounting%20this%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20medical%20data%20and%20disability-related%20data%20are%20high-quality%20because%20they%20were%20verified%20by%20doctors.%20And%20since%20the%20purpose%20was%20to%20register%20people%20for%20disability%20certificates%20to%20make%20them%20eligible%20for%20the%20department%E2%80%99s%20schemes%2C%20only%20those%20fields%20were%20made%20mandatory%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20even%20among%20the%20benefits%20offered%20by%20the%20DEPwD%2C%20four%20of%20the%20seven%20initiatives%20are%20related%20to%20special%20education%20and%20vocational%20training%20programmes%2C%20skill%20training%20and%20scholarships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20data%20released%20by%20the%20government%20includes%20district-wise%2C%20gender-wise%2C%20disability%20type-wise%20and%20age-wise%20information%20and%20will%20be%20updated%20every%20quarter%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20had%20added%20that%20the%20UDID%20database%20was%20also%20meant%20to%20help%20design%20accessible%20websites%20and%20applications%20and%20%E2%80%9Cconnect%20PwDs%20to%20digital%20India%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20nowhere%20in%20the%20UDID%20form%20is%20any%20section%20seeking%20information%20on%20existing%20computer%2C%20mobile%2C%20and%20Internet%20usage%20among%20PwDs%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20already%20been%20under%20attack%20from%20experts%2C%20activists%2C%20and%20Opposition%20leaders%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funion-government-defends-decision-to-remove-questions-on-disability-from-nfhs-6%5C%22%3Edroppin