%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fodisha%2F2023%2Fsep%2F17%2Fgita-mehta-eminent-author-odisha-cm-naveen-patnaiks-sister-no-more-2615554.html%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20made%20her%20decision%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cthinking%20of%20my%20brother%2C%20not%20wishing%20to%20cause%20him%20any%20embarrassment%20at%20a%20sensitive%20time%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20face%20accusations%20that%20nepotism%20might%20have%20been%20brought%20to%20bear%20to%20get%20me%20the%20award%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMehta%20was%20the%20daughter%20of%20Biju%20Patnaik%20and%20the%20sister%20of%20Odisha%20chief%20minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik.%20She%20was%20married%20to%20American%20publisher%20Sonny%20Mehta%2C%20who%20died%20in%20December%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20senior%20politicians%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20express%20their%20condolences%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694948405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17162128%2FF6NiAQgWAAAonsV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Frenowned-writer-gita-mehta-passes-away%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mehta%20had%20written%20books%20including%20Karma%20Cola%2C%20Snakes%20and%20Ladders%2C%20A%20River%20Sutra%2C%20Raj%20and%20Eternal%20Ganesha.%20She%20also%20produced%20and%20directed%20at%20least%2014%20television%20documentaries%20for%20UK%2C%20European%20and%20US%20networks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Frenowned-writer-gita-mehta-passes-away%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2233%20pilots%2C%2097%20cabin-crew%20members%20found%20drunk%20on%20duty%20in%20H1%20of%202023%3A%20DGCA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694947951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-04%2F16%2Ffull%2F1650047686-0933.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2F33-pilots-97-cabin-crew-members-found-drunk-on-duty-in-h1-of-2023-dgca-123091700569_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20DGCA%20rules%2C%20pilots%20and%20cabin%20crew%20members%20must%20undergo%20pre-flight%20breathalyzer%20tests%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2F33-pilots-97-cabin-crew-members-found-drunk-on-duty-in-h1-of-2023-dgca-123091700569_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2F33-pilots-97-cabin-crew-members-found-drunk-on-duty-in-h1-of-2023-dgca-123091700569_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2F33-pilots-97-cabin-crew-members-found-drunk-on-duty-in-h1-of-2023-dgca-123091700569_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Police%20Struggles%20to%20Solve%20Mystery%20of%20Brutal%20Attack%20on%20Female%20Head%20Constable%20in%20a%20Train%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17161149%2Fengin-akyurt-sxjGiW5MDrg-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CShe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20remember%20much%20about%20the%20incident.%20She%20was%20not%20even%20able%20to%20identify%20us%20properly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul%20(name%20changed).%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20since%20his%20elder%20sister%2C%20a%20head%20constable%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%2C%20was%20found%20lying%20unconscious%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20under%20the%20seat%20of%20a%20train%20near%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20puzzled%20authorities%20as%20they%20are%20still%20unable%20to%20trace%20the%20culprits%20or%20a%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20has%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20BJP-ruled%20state%20as%20well%20as%20the%20safety%20provided%20by%20the%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllahabad%20high%20court%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20took%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20is%20monitoring%20the%20investigation.%20The%20UP%20police%2C%20the%20Railway%20police%20and%20the%20UP%20police%20Special%20Task%20Force%20are%20probing%20the%20case%2C%20which%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20high-profile%20whodunnit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2047-year-old%20woman%20head%20constable%20Roshni%20(name%20changed)%20is%20recovering%20in%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Lucknow%20but%20is%20still%20unable%20to%20coherently%20recall%20the%20incident%20due%20to%20injuries%20to%20her%20head%2C%20her%20family%20and%20police%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20met%20her%20after%20she%20regained%20consciousness%2C%20she%20said%20she%20could%20recognise%20my%20face%20but%20could%20not%20remember%20my%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2016%2C%20the%20UP%20police%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20anyone%20who%20would%20provide%20information%20about%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20August%2030%20and%2031.%20Roshni%2C%20who%20is%20posted%20as%20a%20head%20constable%20in%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Sultanpur%20district%2C%20was%20aboard%20the%20Saryu%20Express%20on%20her%20way%20to%20duty%20at%20the%20Hanuman%20Gadi%20Sawan%20Mela%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Due%20to%20some%20reasons%2C%20she%20missed%20her%20stop%20and%20reached%20the%20final%20destination%2C%20Mankapur%20railway%20station%2C%20from%20where%20she%20took%20the%20train%20back%20towards%20Ayodhya.%20However%2C%20between%20these%20two%20stations%2C%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20some%20unknown%20person(s)%20with%20sharp%20objects%2C%20leaving%20her%20badly%20injured%2C%20bleeding%20and%20unconscious%20under%20a%20berth%20in%20one%20of%20the%20coaches.%20On%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20complaint%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Government%20Railway%20Police%2C%20Cantonment%20police%20station%2C%20in%20Ayodhya%20against%20unknown%20persons%20under%20charges%20including%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20assault%20or%20use%20of%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20ruled%20out%20sexual%20assault%20as%20the%20medico-legal%20test%20and%20forensic%20investigation%20have%20not%20confirmed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%204%2C%20UP%20DGP%20Vijay%20Kumar%20and%20special%20DG%20law%20and%20order%20Prashant%20Kumar%20both%20said%20the%20case%20would%20be%20solved%20soon%20and%20the%20real%20culprits%20would%20be%20arrested.%20Officer%20Prashant%20Kumar%20along%20with%20principal%20secretary%20(home)%20Sanjay%20Prasad%20visited%20the%20injured%20woman%20constable%20at%20the%20trauma%20centre%20of%20the%20King%20George%E2%80%99s%20Medical%20University%20in%20Lucknow.%20UP%20police%20along%20with%20railway%20officials%20even%20conducted%20a%20scene%20recreation%20exercise%20of%20the%20incident%20on%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20police%20are%20yet%20to%20solve%20the%20mystery.%20Roshni%20is%20a%20native%20of%20Prayagraj%20district.%20Rahul%2C%20a%20farmer%2C%20says%20his%20sister%20had%20no%20personal%20enmity%20with%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20have%20any%20information%20or%20suspicion%20that%20this%20could%20happen.%20There%20was%20no%20enmity%20nor%20did%20she%20receive%20any%20threats%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20presumes%20that%20someone%20known%20to%20her%20must%20have%20tracked%20down%20her%20routine%20and%20planned%20the%20assault.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20possibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%203%2C%20high%20court%20chief%20justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20and%20Justice%20Ashutosh%20Srivastava%20took%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgruesome%20incident%E2%80%9D%20and%20directed%20the%20court%20registry%20to%20register%20the%20matter%20as%20a%20criminal%20public%20interest%20litigation.%20The%20court%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state.%20The%20case%20was%20brought%20to%20CJ%20Diwaker%E2%80%99s%20attention%20by%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20he%20received%20from%20an%20advocate%20Ram%20Kaushik%20at%20around%203%3A35%20pm%20on%20Sunday%2C%20September%203%2C%20following%20which%20the%20CJ%20constituted%20a%20bench%20at%208%20pm%20at%20his%20residence%20to%20hear%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20petition%2C%20advocate%20Kaushik%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9CRailway%20Authorities%20have%20completely%20failed%20to%20implement%20the%20various%20safety%20measures%20involving%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20women.%20The%20present%20incident%20clearly%20shows%20the%20utter%20violation%20of%20the%20certain%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20also%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20failed%20in%20discharge%20of%20their%20duties%20and%20responsibilities%20in%20giving%20effect%20to%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20formulated%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20passengers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diwaker%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20summoned%20the%20investigation%20officer%20of%20the%20case%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20September%204%20with%20the%20case%20diary.%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(GRP)%20Pooja%20Yadav%20appeared%20in%20court%20and%20informed%20the%20judges%20that%20five%20teams%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20circle%20officer%20and%20deputy-SP%20had%20been%20formed%20to%20solve%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInjuries%20were%20inflicted%20upon%20Roshni%E2%80%99s%20face%20and%20upper%20body%20parts%20with%20a%20sharp-edged%20weapon%2C%20presumably%20a%20chopper%2C%20said%20Yadav.%20The%20court%20took%20note%20of%20the%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20said%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20doubt%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20proceeding%20in%20the%20right%20track%20and%20would%20bring%20results%20fast%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20woman%20constable%E2%80%99s%20statement%20under%20Sections%20161%20or%20164%20of%20the%20CrPC%20was%20yet%20to%20be%20recorded%20since%20she%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20present%20herself%20before%20the%20concerned%20magistrate.%20The%20court%20then%20directed%20the%20concerned%20magistrate%20to%20visit%20the%20woman%20in%20the%20hospital%20to%20record%20her%20statement%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20by%20the%20next%20date.%20The%20judges%20also%20directed%20that%20a%20team%20of%20five%20doctors%2C%20including%20three%20senior%20gynaecologists%2C%20examine%20the%20injured%20head%20constable%20and%20submit%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVed%20Prakash%20Srivastava%2C%20the%20STF%20officer%20investigating%20the%20attack%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20September%2017%20that%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20yet%20to%20be%20recorded%20as%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20clearly%20narrate%20details%20due%20to%20a%20head%20injury%20received%20by%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20visited%20her%20yesterday%20along%20with%20a%20doctor.%20She%20was%20saying%20random%20things%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20remember%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20still%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblind%20case%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Srivastava.%20The%20STF%20is%20probing%20all%20angles%3A%20whether%20she%20had%20any%20personal%20enmity%2C%20if%20the%20assailant(s)%20were%20hired%20by%20someone%20or%20if%20it%20was%20a%20random%20crime.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20into%20all%20possibilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srivastava%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20verifying%20possible%20suspects%20but%20are%20yet%20to%20pinpoint%20anyone.%20The%20woman%20head%20constable%20is%20so%20far%20the%20only%20witness%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694947361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17161149%2Fengin-akyurt-sxjGiW5MDrg-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-struggles-to-solve-mystery-of-brutal-attack-on-female-head-constable-in-a-train%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20case%20has%20puzzled%20authorities%20as%20they%20are%20still%20unable%20to%20trace%20the%20culprits%20or%20a%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20has%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20BJP-ruled%20state%20as%20well%20as%20the%20safety%20provided%20by%20the%20Railways.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-struggles-to-solve-mystery-of-brutal-attack-on-female-head-constable-in-a-train%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dozens%20of%20people%20injured%20in%20violence%20at%20Eritrean%20cultural%20festival%20in%20Germany%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694947020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-germany-stuttgart-eritrea_6288097.jpg%3F20230917114344%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdozens-of-people-injured-in-violence-at-eritrean-cultural-festival-in-germany-12963400%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Clashes%20between%20Eritrean%20government%20supporters%20and%20opponents%20at%20a%20cultural%20festival%20in%20Germany%20has%20left%20dozens%20injured%2C%20including%20at%20least%2026%20police%20officers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A131%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdozens-of-people-injured-in-violence-at-eritrean-cultural-festival-in-germany-12963400%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fst