20researcher%2C%20Tara%20Sepehri%20Far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20it%20would%20sanction%20over%20two%20dozen%20individuals%20and%20entities%20with%20ties%20to%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cviolent%20suppression%E2%80%9D%20of%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMahsa%E2%80%99s%20story%20did%20not%20end%20with%20her%20brutal%20death.%20She%20inspired%20a%20historic%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20Woman%2C%20Life%2C%20Freedom%20%E2%80%94%20that%20has%20impacted%20Iran%20and%20influenced%20people%20across%20the%20globe%2C%E2%80%9D%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20protests%20are%20also%20planned%20on%20Saturday%20in%20many%20cities%20across%20the%20world%20to%20commemorate%20the%20anniversary%2C%20including%20in%20Washington%20and%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20rights%20groups%2C%20more%20than%20500%20people%20have%20died%20in%20the%20crackdown%20on%20protesters%20in%20Iran%2C%20while%20thousands%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Seven%20more%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-executes-3-men-linked-to-amini-protests%2Fa-65673839%5C%22%3Eexecuted%20by%20Iranian%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20relation%20to%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Famini-family-barred-from-marking-anniversary-rights-groups%2Fa-66832784%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694938540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17132823%2Fe52036fc-5334-48c6-810f-305ab71d7e95.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flate-iranian-activist-mahsa-aminis-family-barred-from-marking-her-first-death-anniversary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amini's%20death%20last%20year%2C%20while%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20had%20sparked%20unprecedented%20protests%20against%20the%