and%20converts%20them%20into%20eco-bricks.%20Our%20kids%20learn%20how%20to%20convert%20plastic%20into%20bricks%20and%20work%20in%20the%20plant%20after%20school.%20We%20pay%20them%20for%20that%20too.%20This%20way%20they%20get%20to%20learn%20an%20extra%20skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eco-bricks%20are%20then%20used%20in%20smaller%20constructions%20in%20and%20around%20the%20school.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20using%20a%20machine%20from%20the%20Netherlands.%20The%20machine%20upcycles%20the%20plastic%20into%20things%20of%20use.%20We%20have%20to%20put%20the%20melted%20plastic%20in%20different%20moulds%20and%20the%20machine%20converts%20it%20into%20pots%2C%20planters%2C%20keyrings%2C%20earnings%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329788%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20eco-bricks%20are%20then%20used%20in%20smaller%20constructions%20in%20and%20around%20the%20school.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Parmita%20Sarma%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2